SUMMARY:Security Slam Awards Ceremony
DESCRIPTION:Come celebrate the winners of the&nbsp\;2026 Security Slam at KubeCon + CloudNativeCon Europe! In the past month\, projects have been competing to improve their security posture. They have been using LFX insights to achieve measurable&nbsp\;security improvements\, while getting support from TAG Security and Compliance. Learn about the tools used in this competition\, and how you can apply them to your own project. Then we will give out awards to the teams that have made the most improvement leading up to&nbsp\;the event.\n\nClick here to see the Security Slam Objective Details:&nbsp\;https://securityslam.com/slam26&nbsp\;
